{"tid":397276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇就職大學POLY份?]全球畢業生就業力 港4大學上榜","createTime":"2017-09-12T10:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T11:14:24.000Z","uid":42425,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd97eddd2a9ef3d15d171b86b17c1ead4d6290b0","tid":397276,"uid":42425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/images/news/content/Image_20170912104656_7856715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fimages%2Fnews%2Fcontent%2FImage_20170912104656_7856715.jpg&h=8ca96222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【經濟日報專訊】高等教育研究機構QS公布2018年全球大學畢業生就業能力排名，香港大學的總評分較2017年上升約10分，惟全球排名反下跌兩名，排第20，被內地一級學府清華大學拋離。<br />\n<br />\n清華大學更成為亞洲區就業能力最強大學。人力資源顧問表示，企業傾向聘用熟悉內地商業文化的內地大學畢業生，令香港大學畢業生的競爭性較弱。<br />\n<br />\n國際高等教育研究機構Quacquarelli Symonds（QS）公布2018年全球500間大學畢業生的就業能力排名，按全球僱主的評價、成功校友的數目、與僱主的合作關係、僱主與該校學生的聯繫，以及畢業生就業率等作評核準則，每項準則以100分為滿分。<br />\n<br />\n港大全球排20 亞洲第3<br />\n本港有4間大學上榜，其中香港大學排名最高，在亞洲第3位，全球排第20位，較上次研究跌兩位，惟其總評分達86.5分，較上次高10分。當中畢業生就業率一項分數最高，達98.5分，較上次研究高約10分，這項目在全球排名第11位；其次為畢業生與僱主的合作關係，獲96.9分；以及僱主與該校學生的聯繫，包括在校園提供職位資訊等，獲95.5分，較上次大幅上升27分。<br />\n<br />\n另外3間上榜的本港大學分別為全球就業能力排名第77位的中文大學；排名第121至130位的城市大學；和第300位以下的浸會大學。全球整體而言，頭3位分別是史丹福大學、加州大學洛杉磯分校和哈佛大學；亞洲地區以清華大學排名最高，亦同時是全球第10位、北京大學位列第23位，復旦大學位列第27位。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/news/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%8A%9B-%E6%B8%AF4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C/878429871?utm_source=170912_news_u&amp;utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_campaign=fbpost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%25B8%25AF4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25A6%259C%2F878429871%3Futm_source%3D170912_news_u%26utm_medium%3Dfb%26utm_campaign%3Dfbpost&d=YjM3M9TPonlzxN2aP1mGO1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=6df88177\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/news/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%8A%9B-%E6%B8%AF4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C/878429871?utm_source=170912_news_u&amp;utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_campaign=fbpost</a>"},{"pid":"f0ba56d303f1d8ae4dcab930577abd6914b79f70","tid":397276,"uid":42425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">城大重返三大帝位</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844db7047519cca274d92e9a57f1a149c83cbab1","tid":397276,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"其實永遠都唔知所謂僱主即係邊d人<br />\ne.g. medic ，咁會唔會打去醫院／律師樓問? <br />\n如果唔會計law/medic/construction related degrees，咁又算唔算就業力"},{"pid":"b0e9f2591fe57133420f2ee203f9a9abb5d52abe","tid":397276,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"科大就業力in terms of banking and finance/ engine 好過城大咁多，<br />\nbank非三大唔請，咁又點解係有city份"},{"pid":"40df8b09bea2b3d1a1f8fda2a4cd5c16b70743fb","tid":397276,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"R撚爆個頭都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696e6b98dda3beab8a1effa77a356145d2d6f8dc","tid":397276,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"又一項研究幫手證明香港只係生活左一堆唔返工就會餓死既奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班上岸既就日日遊山玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820b095b33952e1657f899dfc72a8355dad68d28","tid":397276,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>科大就業力in terms of banking and finance/ engine 好過城大咁多，<br />\nbank非三大唔請，咁又點解係有city份</blockquote><br />\n好疑惑，點解ust唔見左<img src=\"/assets/fac